{"word":"G5576 - ψευδομαρτυρέω - pseudomartyréō - psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o - Be a false witness","slug":"G5576","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψευδομαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pseudomartyréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be a false witness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C8;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - pseudomartureo&#x0304;</b> - <i>psyoo-dom-ar-too-reh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>; to <i>be an untrue testifier</i>, that is, offer <i>falsehood in evidence:</i> - be a false witness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5571\">G5571</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572\">G5572</a>, <a href=\"#/G5573\">G5573</a>, <a href=\"#/G5574\">G5574</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>, <a href=\"#/G5578\">G5578</a>, <a href=\"#/G5579\">G5579</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580\">G5580</a>, <a href=\"#/G5581\">G5581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5582\">G5582</a>, <a href=\"#/G5583\">G5583</a>, <a href=\"#/G893\">G893</a>"}]}